DESCRIPTION:It’s nice to do things in real life isn’t it? After two cri
 tically acclaimed shows at the Edinburgh Fringe in 2024 and 2025\, multi-aw
 ard winning comedian Alex Kitson has a brand new hour of stand-up comedy to
  show the people of Camden (before he gets on the train up north for 2026).
  He's talking about attention - so if if you could direct yours his way for
  a moment he'd be very grateful. Praise for Alex Kitson: Best Reviewed Show
 s of the Edinburgh Fringe 2025 “The future of British comedy ” - ★★
